1a:T44c,Internal evidence provides clear product description: oxidized regenerated cellulose in tuft form for hemostasis. Brochure description specifies mechanism (low acidic pH), form factor (soft tufts), hemostasis time (2-4 minutes), antibacterial properties, and specific use case (neurosurgical procedures, hard-to-reach/irregularly shaped sites). Division assignment (Endo Surgery) and category (Hemostatic Agents) align with product function. Entity is clearly a product family/line within hemostatic agents. However, brand field is empty and no external verification available. MERIZELLE appears to be the brand/product line name, but manufacturer attribution to Meril Life Sciences cannot be independently verified without external sources. Classification data is internally consistent and clinically coherent. Recommended for review to: (1) confirm brand/manufacturer attribution, (2) verify MERIZELLE is indeed Meril Life Sciences product, (3) confirm no trademark or naming conflicts exist. Product meaning itself is unambiguous - this is an ORC-based topical hemostatic agent in fiber/tuft form.16:["$","$L19",null,{"product":{"product_name":"MERIZELLE Fiber","product_name_display":"MERIZELLE Fiber","sku_code":"MRL-HEM-002","product_family":"MERIZELLE Fiber","product_family_display":"Merizelle Fiber","slug":"merizelle-fiber","images":[{"id":"prop_69c4bba","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c4b442ffa53c7211ead57b/cover_b730b114.jpg","original_filename":"cover_merizelle_1665144119pdf_5e0ca6a9c1.pdf.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":335206,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26T05:59:00.484818+00:00","source":"family_propagation","width":1654,"height":2339}],"status":"published","live_visible":true,"brochure_url":"","seo_meta_title":"MERIZELLE Fiber | MERIZELLE Hemostatic Agents - MedDevice Pro Telangana","seo_meta_description":"Tufts of soft lightweight oxidized regenerated cellulose for hard-to-reach or irregularly shaped bleeding sites, suitable for neurosurgical procedures